  <!-- ========================= -->
  <!-- DYNAMIC SEO PAGES -->
  <!-- ========================= -->

  <!-- IMPORTANT:
  These URLs should NOT remain manual in real SaaS production.

  Must be auto-generated dynamically from database using backend cron/build process.

  Dynamic URLs include:

  1. Individual Property Listings
     /listing/:id

  Example:
  https://gruvora.com/listing/65fd71ab29f9

  2. Owner Public Profiles
     /owner/:id

  Example:
  https://gruvora.com/owner/65ad921bb8e2

  3. Future Blog Pages
     /blog/:slug

  4. Future City Landing Pages
     /city/:name

  5. Future Verified Business Profiles
     /business/:id

  Production Rule:
  Backend should generate dynamic sitemap automatically
  using MongoDB data and refresh periodically.

  Recommended:
  Split into:
  - sitemap.xml
  - sitemap-listings.xml
  - sitemap-owners.xml
  - sitemap-blog.xml

  for better scalability and Google crawl efficiency.
  -->

